          <details class="faq-item reveal" name="faq-sm">
            <summary class="faq-q">How many posts per week do you create?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a"><p>Depends on your package: Growth includes 3 posts per week, Dominate includes 5 posts per week across up to 3 platforms. Every post is strategically planned — no filler content.</p></div>
